Russia RTS Stock-Index Futures Gain at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-04-07T15:18:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/russia-rts-stock-index-futures-gain-at-start-of-trading.html
Russia ’s RTS stock-index futures
expiring in June gained 0.3 percent to 204,460 by 11:02 a.m. in
 New York .  Contracts on OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest oil
producer, rose 0.3 percent. Contracts on OAO Sberbank, Russia’s
largest lender, were little changed. OAO Gazprom, the natural-
gas export monopoly, gained 0.1 percent. The Market Vectors
Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that holds Russian shares, fell
0.8 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
